dct_title_s: Mallard Island at Manahawkin, New Jersey, Stafford Township, Ocean County
dct_description_sm: This map shows property lots on Mallard Island that are linked to Monobay Inc Developers. A handwritten inscription indicates this as a tax map.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Township Committee members signed off on the map but the names are not clearly legible.
An inscription states A-13-1 Tax Maps.
